data.description: Gorgeous two story home built in 2017 - backing to a preserve at the end of a cul-de-sac in popular Timberlake subdivision! Neutral color palette, wrought iron balusters, tile floors, crown molding, & tons of natural light! Beautiful island kitchen with bar seating, granite counters, rich brown cabinets, stainless steel appliances, under-mount stainless steel sink, & Edison pendant lights. Open layout opens up to the main gathering living room & separate dining room perfect for entertaining. Downstairs Master suite has tray ceilings double sink vanity, garden tub & separate glass shower, with a large walk-in closet. Upstairs has a HUGE game room, making it the perfect second living space retreat. Three additional bedrooms share a hall bathroom with two sinks. The garage boasts upgraded flooring, perfect for an at home gym. Relax on your covered patio with a huge fenced in backyard with preserve views.
